oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Alkahest Attractions, Inc. Job No. 38196
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2767) for an order placed by Alakahest Attractions, Inc. for 150 three color jumbos, 2 one color jumbos (three sheets), 5 one column mats, and 5 two column mats for a performance at the Asheville Auditorium on May 15. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
